[
  {
    "startTime": 3.3,
    "endTime": 5.3,
    "text": "[Caine] Saying goodbyes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.4,
    "endTime": 8.4,
    "text": "[John] Saying hello."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.6,
    "endTime": 10.899999999999999,
    "text": "[Caine] You think your wife can hear you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.053,
    "endTime": 12.200000000000001,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.4,
    "endTime": 15.8,
    "text": "Then why bother?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.0,
    "endTime": 20.8,
    "text": "Maybe I'm wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.0,
    "endTime": 23.2,
    "text": "You're going to die."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.315,
    "endTime": 24.400000000000002,
    "text": "Maybe not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.6,
    "endTime": 29.400000000000002,
    "text": "♪ Goodbye to you my trusted friend ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.6,
    "endTime": 31.5,
    "text": "A new day is dawning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.7,
    "endTime": 35.9,
    "text": "New ideas, new rules, new management."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.2,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "♪ We've known each other since we were nine or ten ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.2,
    "endTime": 42.1,
    "text": "Who is this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.3,
    "endTime": 44.3,
    "text": "The Marquis de Gramont."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.6,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "Challenge him to single combat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.2,
    "endTime": 51.300000000000004,
    "text": "Win or lose, it's a way out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.426,
    "endTime": 53.4,
    "text": "I don't sit at The Table."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.5,
    "endTime": 54.9,
    "text": "Your family does."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.0,
    "endTime": 58.5,
    "text": "♪ Please pray for me ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.7,
    "endTime": 62.271,
    "text": "♪ I was the black sheep of the family ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.271,
    "endTime": 66.2,
    "text": "A man has to look his best when it's time to get married..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.316,
    "endTime": 67.7,
    "text": "or buried."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.9,
    "endTime": 70.2,
    "text": "I'm going to need a gun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.4,
    "endTime": 74.94900000000001,
    "text": "♪ Goodbye my friend, it's hard to die ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.7,
    "endTime": 87.2,
    "text": "If you win, The Table will honor it's word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.2,
    "endTime": 89.4,
    "text": "You will have your freedom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.6,
    "endTime": 92.1,
    "text": "♪ It's hard to die ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.3,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "Under the old laws, only one can survive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.2,
    "endTime": 98.10000000000001,
    "text": "Failure to meet at sunrise..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.2,
    "endTime": 99.60000000000001,
    "text": "♪ It's hard to die ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.8,
    "endTime": 104.7,
    "text": "will result in execution."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.9,
    "endTime": 106.60000000000001,
    "text": "[John] Last words, Winston?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.8,
    "endTime": 108.317,
    "text": "Just have fun out there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.4,
    "endTime": 114.10000000000001,
    "text": "♪ We had joy ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.4,
    "endTime": 116.5,
    "text": "♪ We had fun ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.7,
    "endTime": 119.8,
    "text": "♪ We had seasons in the sun ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.3,
    "text": "I want you to find your peace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.5,
    "endTime": 131.2,
    "text": "But a good death only comes after a good life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.5,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": "You and I left a good life behind a long time ago, my friend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.9,
    "endTime": 144.061,
    "text": "♪ It's hard to die ♪"
  }
]